title: ASB Transcriptomics Skill Collection v1
abstract: Curated, evidence-grounded skills and software-tool records for computational transcriptomics, assembled by the AgenticScienceBuilder pipeline from open-access method papers. Each skill is deduplicated across papers, anchored to verbatim evidence spans, and annotated with EDAM IRIs.
